#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour48.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.8 tour"
msgstr "Visita Xfce 4.8"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to all the new major visual features in Xfce 4.8. This is only the visual part of what has been done; for a full list of changes, see the [changelogs](/download/changelogs/).\n"
msgstr "Aquesta visita vous fera descobrir totas las novèlas caracteristicas majeures visualas dins Xfce 4.8. Ce n'est que la partie visible d'aqueste que es estada fait, per una lista completa dels modificacions, veire la [ liste dels cambiaments](/download/changelogs/).\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Remote shares browsing"
msgstr "Partages distants"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thunar now has optional support for GVFS which will allow you to browse remote shares using Thunar: FTP, Windows Shares, WebDav and SSH servers...\n"
msgstr "Thunar a ara un supòrt opcional per GVFS  que vos permetrà de percórrer los partiment s distants en utilizant Thunar : FTP, partiment Windows, WebDAV e servidors SSH ...\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar browsing a remote share][img-thunar-remote]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar percor un partiment distant][img-thunar-remote]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "New file operations progress dialog"
msgstr "Fenèstra de progression de las operacions Novèl fichièr"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "When several file operations (copy or move) are being handled in parallel, Thunar now shows a single progress dialog which displays all the relevant information.\n"
msgstr "Quand mantuna operacion suls fichièrs (copiar o desplaçar) son tractadas en parallèl, Thunar aficha d'ara enlà una bóstia de dialòg de progression unica qu'aficha totas las informacions pertinentas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Progress dialog][img-thunar-progress]\n"
msgstr "![Fenèstra Progression][img-thunar-progress]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "Eject button for removable devices"
msgstr "Boton d'ejeccion pels periferics amovibles"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is is now possible to eject removable devices by clicking the eject button near each removable device label in the side pane.\n"
msgstr "Es ara possible d'ejectar de periferics amovibles en clicant sul boton d'ejeccion prèp de l'etiqueta de cada periferic amovible dins lo panèl lateral.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Eject button][img-thunar-eject]\n"
msgstr "![Boton d'ejeccion][img-thunar-eject]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Xfce panel has been totally rewritten in 4.8, here are the most visible changes.\n"
msgstr "Lo panèl Xfce es estada totalament reescrich dins 4.8, aquí los cambiaments los mai visibles.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved positioning and size handling"
msgstr "Melhorament de la manipulacion del posicionament e de la talha"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel has much better support for positioning panels on the screen. It can be dragged and snapped to screen borders; floating positions are only remembered when moving a panel and the length of the panel can be adjusted as a percentage of the monitor size.\n"
msgstr "Lo panèl a un melhor supòrt dels posicionaments dels panèls sus l'ecran. Pòt èsser desplaçat e se metre al bòrds de l'ecran, las posicions flotantas son solament rapeladas al moment del desplaçament del panèl e la longor del panèl pòt èsser ajustada en tant que percentatge de la talha de l'ecran.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:37
#, no-wrap
msgid "Transparent backgrounds"
msgstr "Fons transparent"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel is now able to draw transparent panel backgrounds with non transparent items. Your panel items will remain readable and you will enjoy a nice panel look.\n"
msgstr "Lo panèl es ara en mesure de dessiner un panèl amb un fons transparent amb dels objets non transparents. Vos elements del panèl demoraràn lisibles e poiretz profiechar d'un look de panèl agréable.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Transparent panel background][img-panel-transparent]\n"
msgstr "![Fons del panèl transparent][img-panel-transparent]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "New item editor"
msgstr "Novèl editor d'article"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel now features an item editor which allows to modify, move, add and remove items quickly. This is particularly useful for items which are hard to right click and gives you an easy way to change your panel layout from a single place.\n"
msgstr "Lo panèl dispausa d'ara enlà d'un editor d'element que permet de modificar, desplaçar, apondre e suprimir dels elements rapidament. Aquò es particulièrement utile pels elements que son difficiles a far amb un clic drech e vous donne un mejan aisit de changer la disposicion de votre panèl dempuèi un seul endroit.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Panel item editor][img-panel-editor]\n"
msgstr "![Editor d'element del panèl][img-panel-editor]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Drag and drop to create launchers"
msgstr "Glisser-depausar per crear d'aviadors"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can now drag and drop menu entries from the panel applications menu, application finder or Thunar to the panel to create launchers. This feature should please the huge number of people who had been requesting it for ages. The launcher also has an integrated application finder to add new items.\n"
msgstr "Podètz ara lisar e depausar las entradas del menú del panèl aplicacions supportant menú, la lista d'aplicacion o Thunar dempuèi lo panèl per crear d'aviadors. Aquesta foncionalitat deuriá plaire al grand nombre de personas que avaient demandé aquò dempuèi longtemps. L'aviador a tanben un listeur d'aplicacion integrada per apondre de novèls elements.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window buttons plugin"
msgstr "Botons de la fenèstra empeuton"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "The iconbox and tasklist plugins are new merged into 1 plugin, called window buttons. It implements different sorting modes, improved handling in vertical panels and can draw a similar frame as Xfwm4 Alt+tab when hovering a button.\n"
msgstr "Los empeutons de la bóstia d’icòna e la lista dels prètzfaits an de novèl fusionat en 1 empeuton, apelat botons de fenèstra. Met en òbra diferents modes de tri, un melhor maniement dins los panèls verticals e pòt dessiner un quadre similar al Alt+tab de Xfwm4 al moment del susvòl d'un boton.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "New fuzzy clock"
msgstr "Novèl relòtge fosca"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "An Xfce release without a new clock mode would not be a true Xfce release. Let us introduce you the 'fuzzy' clock mode!\n"
msgstr "Una version Xfce sens un novèl mòde de relòtge ne serait pas una vraie version de Xfce. Laissez-nous vous présenter lo mòde de relòtge 'fosc' !\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New fuzzy clock mode][img-panel-fuzzy-clock]\n"
msgstr "![Novèl mòde de relòtge fosc][img-panel-fuzzy-clock]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "New directory menu plugin"
msgstr "Novèl repertòri menú empeuton "

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "The directory menu plugin provides a menu reproducing the arborescence of a particular folder. This allows you to open a terminal or a file manager in a sub-folder in a very fast and efficient way.\n"
msgstr "L'empeuton menú repertòri prepausa un menú que reprodusís l'arborescéncia d'un dorsièr particular. Aquò vos permet de dobrir un terminal o d'un gestionari de fichièrs dins un sosdorsièr d'una manièra fòrça rapida e eficaça.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Directory menu plugin][img-panel-directorymenu]\n"
msgstr "![Repertòri menú empeuton][img-panel-directorymenu]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "Applications menu edition"
msgstr "Edicion menú Aplicacions"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can now edit the applications menu using any Freedesktop compliant menu editor, Alacarte being the one we used to test.\n"
msgstr "Podètz ara editar lo menú de las aplicacions en utilizant quin editor de menú que siá, compatible Freedesktop, Alacarte essent lo qu'avèm utilizat per testar.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:75
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved multihead setup configuration"
msgstr "Melhorament de la configuracion d'installacion multiecrans"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce can now handle and setup multihead setups for any randr 1.2 compatible driver. Unfortunately, this means it will not work with Nvidia proprietary drivers.\n"
msgstr "Xfce pòt ara manipuler e configurar las configuracions multiecrans per n'importe quel pilòt compatible randr 1.2. Malheureusement, aquò significa que foncionarà pas amb los pilòts proprietaris Nvidia.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can enable and disable plugged screens, set their resolution, refresh rate, rotation and reflection, clone screens or extend desktops.\n"
msgstr "Podètz activar e desactivar los ecrans brancats, fixer lor resolucion, lor taus de refrescament, la rotacion e la reflexion, cloner dels ecrans o de étendre los burèus.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New display settings dialog][img-display-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Novèla fenèstra dels paramètres d'afichatge][img-display-settings]\n"

#. type: Title ####
#: content/about/tour48.md:83
#, no-wrap
msgid "Timed confirmation"
msgstr "Confirmacion cronometrada"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "Any change made with the settings dialog will have to be confirmed within ten seconds or they will be reverted. This prevents broken video drivers from leaving your computer unusable.\n"
msgstr "Toute modificacion aportada a la bóstia de dialòg dels reglatges devra èsser confirmada dins las dix segondas o ils seràn anullats. Aquò empêche los pilòts vidéo copats de quitar vòstre ordenador inutilizable.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Timed confirmation for display settings changes][img-display-settings-confirmation]\n"
msgstr "![Confirmacion cronometrat pel cambiament dels paramètres d'afichatge ][img-display-settings-confirmation]\n"

#. type: Title ####
#: content/about/tour48.md:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Quick setup dialog"
msgstr "Fenèstra de configuracion rapide"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "The quick setup dialog allows you to configure a dual screen setup in a second. Plug the second screen, press the display key or Windows + p and select the wanted layout. Done!\n"
msgstr "La bóstia de dialòg de configuracion rapide vos permet de configurar una configuracion double ecran en una segonda. Brancatz lo segond ecran, quichatz sus la tòca ecran o Windows + p e seleccionatz la mesa en pagina desirada. Es fait !\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Quick multihead setup][img-minimal-display-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Installacion rapide multimonitor][img-minimal-display-settings]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:95
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings edition in the Xfce Settings Editor"
msgstr "Edicion Paramètres dins l'editor de paramètres Xfce"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Xfce Settings Editor now deserves its name, it is no longer a simpler Xfconf settings viewer. You can now modify, delete, add and reset settings through its interface. It also monitors changes to update its view.\n"
msgstr "L'editor de paramètres Xfce mérite d'ara enlà son nom, il n'est mai un simple spectateur de paramètres xfconf. Podètz ara modificar, suprimir, apondre e reïnicializar los paramètres pel biais de son interfàcia. Il surveille tanben los cambiaments de metre a jorn son punt de vista.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Editing Xfconf properties with the Settings Editor][img-settings-editor]\n"
msgstr "![Edicion dels proprietats de Xfconf amb l'Editor de paramètres][img-settings-editor]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:101
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved keyboard layout selection"
msgstr "Melhorament de la seleccion de la configuracion del clavièr"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:104
#, no-wrap
msgid "The layout selection dialog received a lot of love: it no longer displays cryptic language/variants codes but uses localized languages/variants names. Layout edition was also made easier by prefilling the dialogs with the current values.\n"
msgstr "La bóstia de dialòg de seleccion de la mesa en pagina a recebut fòrça atencion : aficha pas mai los còdis de lenga / variantas cryptiques mas utiliza de langages / variantas de noms localizats. La disposicion de l'édition a tanben été facilitée pel preemplenatge dels bóstia de dialòg amb las valors courantes.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Layouts and variants list][img-keyboard-settings-list]\n"
msgstr "![Organizacions e la lista dels variantas][img-keyboard-settings-list]\n"

